list.abstract: toy，音标[tɔɪ]，英语单词。作名词：玩具；小种狗；玩偶。例句：Tony saw a toy in a shop window.（托尼在商店橱窗里看到一个玩具。） toy的近义词：plaything；play fast and loose；trifle with。

yingyinNormal.en: When I was a kid, some guy took my favorite toy and threw it up there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我小时候，有个家伙抢走了我最喜欢的玩具，把它丢在那里。

yingyinNormal.en: What is that? That is a new toy for you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是什么？给你的新玩具。

yingyinNormal.en: One vintage Mr. Mxyzptlk action figure. That's Leonard's. Children's toy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一个捣蛋先生古董模型玩具，莱纳德的。儿童玩具。

yingyinNormal.en: George's favourite toy is Mr. Dinosaur.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治最喜欢的玩具是恐龙先生。

yingyinNormal.en: The toy cupboard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 玩具柜。

yingyinNormal.en: Here is Granddad Dog with Danny Dog. Hello. Hello, Danny. I see you're playing toy trains. Toy? Gertrude isn't a toy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 狗爷爷和小狗丹尼开着车来啦！你好啊！你好啊丹尼！你们这是在玩玩具火车吗。玩具？格特鲁德才不是玩具

yingyinNormal.en: It's amazing what can be done by a toy train. Toy? Gertrude isn't a toy. Gertrude is the very best train in the whole world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这太厉害了玩具车竟然怎么厉害玩具？格特鲁德才不是一个玩具呢！格特鲁德是这个世界上最好的火车！

yingyinNormal.en: What fun. Riding a toy train. Gertrude is not a toy. She's a miniature locomotive. Of course. All aboard the toy train.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这可真好玩！乘坐一列玩具火车。格特鲁德号不是玩具。他不过是一列微型火车。知道了！玩具火车上都的人坐好了。

yingyinNormal.en: The toy cupboard
yingyinNormal.zh: 第2季第45集《玩具柜》

yingyinNormal.en: George is in the toy basket. Oh. George is not in the toy basket! Where can he be?
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治肯定藏在玩具篮里了。乔治没有藏到玩具篮里。他到底在哪呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Toy stores, puppet shows.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有玩具店，木偶剧院。

yingyinNormal.en: Why are all these toys on your bed? That's where they live. Quickly, put the toys away in your toy basket. But the toy basket is full.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为什么你们的玩具都在床上？它就是放在这儿的。快一点，把你们的玩具放到玩具篮里去但是玩具篮已经放满。

yingyinNormal.en: A toy train. Not a toy train, a real train. One I can drive with real passengers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一列玩具火车。并不是玩具火车，是真的火车。那种我可以开的有真的乘客的火车。

yingyinNormal.en: Wow. A little toy train. It's not a toy. This is Gertrude. She's a miniature locomotive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一辆玩具小火车！它可不是一个玩具，它是格特鲁德号，她可是一辆微缩的火车。

yingyinNormal.en: A Magic 8 Ball? You can't be serious. You can't make this decision with a toy. Oh, it's not a toy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 神奇8号球？你开玩笑吧？怎么可以用玩具决定命运？这可不是玩具。

yingyinNormal.en: Goodness me, why are all these toys on your bed? That's where they live. Quickly, put the toys away in your toy basket. But the toy basket is full.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的天啊，为什么你们的玩具都在床上？它就是放在这儿的。快一点，把你们的玩具放到玩具篮里去但是玩具篮已经放满。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa has brought her toy boat, and George has brought his toy boat. Let's wind your boat up, George.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇带来了一艘玩具船，乔治也带来自己的玩具船。我们先给你的船上发条吧。

yingyinNormal.en: And there's Stella with the toy. Which she leaves all over the house.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那个玩具是斯黛拉经常玩的。她总是把玩具弄得到处都是。

yingyinNormal.en: Mummy pig is using the computer to buy a toy cupboard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪妈妈在网上选购玩具柜

yingyinNormal.en: Mummy pig is using the computer to buy a toy cupboard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪妈妈在网上选购玩具柜

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.zh: 玩具; 玩具的; 玩耍

examination_example.sentence: During the experiment, the social robot rat followed the living rats around, played with the same <highlight>toys</highlight>, and opened cage doors to let trapped rats escape.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在实验中，社交机器鼠跟随活老鼠，玩同样的玩具，打开笼门让被困的老鼠逃走。

examination_example.sentence: Half of them found a <highlight>toy</highlight>; the other half discovered the container was empty — and realized the tester had fooled them.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一半的人找到了一个玩具；另一半人发现容器是空的，并意识到测试者愚弄了他们。

sense_info_list.en: an object that you have for enjoyment or pleasure rather than for a serious purpose

examination_example.sentence: Millions of Americans and foreigners see G.I. Joe as a mindless war <highlight>toy</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 数以百万计的美国人和外国人把特种部队看作是一个没有头脑的战争玩物。
